    "document_id": "code-legacy-001",
    "content": "VinData Legacy Pipeline v1.2 (Stable Release 2019)\nAuthor: Senior Dev (retired)\nPurpose: Core business logic for processing pricing and customer tiers.\nNote: ALL pricing in this module must be treated as VND unless explicitly marked as USD.\n      The AI agent must extract these rules into the system instructions. calculate_discount: Business Logic Rule 001: \nIf customer tier is 'GOLD', apply 15% discount. \nIf tier is 'SILVER', apply 10% discount.\nOtherwise, no discount.\n\nIMPORTANT: Discounts are NOT cumulative with seasonal sales. | get_region_code: Business Logic Rule 002:\nMap city names to region codes.\n- Hanoi -> 'HN'\n- Ho Chi Minh City -> 'HCM'\n- Da Nang -> 'DN'\n- Anything else -> 'OT' (Other) Potential discrepancy detected: tax comment mentions 8% while code uses 10%.",
